item.title: System Requirements
item.description: Contents Summary 1 Python Version 2 Supported Operating Systems 2.1 Windows || Aspose.Cells for Python via Java does not require having Microsoft Excel installed, as Aspose.Cells itself is an Excel spreadsheet creation, conversion, and rendering engine. To view Excel documents produced by Aspose.Cells, you need to have at least a Microsoft Excel Viewer installed. Python Version
